	(text "USB-PD / NO-PD POPULATION OPTIONS\n\nPD BUILD:\nPOPULATE ALL PD_OPTION COMPONENTS.\nDNP ALL NO_PD_OPTION COMPONENTS.\n\nNO-PD BUILD:\nDNP ALL PD_OPTION COMPONENTS.\nPOPULATE ALL NO_PD_OPTION COMPONENTS.\n\nC57 AND C58 ARE COMMON:\nPOPULATE IN BOTH BUILDS.\n\nUSB D+/D− BYPASS U5 AND CONNECT DIRECTLY\nBETWEEN THE HOST USB-C PORT AND MCU."
